that exposure at all
costs; you know,

00:06:32.630 --> 00:06:34.200
I don't really care
what the contract says.

00:06:34.200 --> 00:06:35.800
I don't really understand it.

00:06:35.800 --> 00:06:37.990
I just want to get
my music out there.

00:06:37.990 --> 00:06:41.080
And so of course something
like YouTube uses that.

00:06:41.080 --> 00:06:43.670
Hey, look at all the
exposure you're going to get.

00:06:43.670 --> 00:06:49.580
So, you know -- so we've so
completely overexposed ourselves,

00:06:49.580 --> 00:06:53.370
