00:07:19.070 --> 00:07:20.710
I forgot what was the --

00:07:20.710 --> 00:07:22.280
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum: Oh,
about artists' rights --

00:07:22.280 --> 00:07:23.580
&gt;&gt; Maria Schneider: Oh
the artists' rights.

00:07:23.580 --> 00:07:24.880
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum: -- [inaudible].

00:07:24.880 --> 00:07:29.000
&gt;&gt; Maria Schneider: So there's
