00:07:59.280 --> 00:08:00.580
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum:
Is it impacting you --

00:08:00.580 --> 00:08:01.880
&gt;&gt; Maria Schneider: Absolutely.

00:08:01.880 --> 00:08:03.180
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum: -- directly?

00:08:03.180 --> 00:08:04.480
&gt;&gt; Maria Schneider:
Well, in different ways.

00:08:04.480 --> 00:08:07.870 position:56%
I notice the impact definitely on
my performance royalties like the --

00:08:07.870 --> 00:08:12.390
you know, the -- Because
now what's happening,

00:08:12.390 --> 00:08:15.640
it used to be that
music had a value.

00:08:15.640 --> 00:08:16.940
Music had a value.

00:08:16.940 --> 00:08:19.420
We said it costs this much
