00:08:24.120 --> 00:08:27.000
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum: So does
this impact you directly?

00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:29.320
&gt;&gt; Maria Schneider: It's
impacted me in a very big way

00:08:29.320 --> 00:08:32.590
and it shaped the way
I do things now.

00:08:32.590 --> 00:08:37.010
So, one of the things that are
going on is that it used to be

00:08:37.010 --> 00:08:41.350
that people set their price,
like this shirt, you know.

00:08:41.350 --> 00:08:42.810 position:56%
What does it cost for the materials?

00:08:42.810 --> 00:08:44.920
What does it cost to make it?

00:08:44.920 --> 00:08:50.740
