pays that to the manufacturer,

00:08:50.740 --> 00:08:54.360
the designer or all those
things and then sells the shirt.

00:08:54.360 --> 00:08:58.040
When you buy the shirt,
they aren't --

00:08:58.040 --> 00:09:02.770
