00:45:09.490 --> 00:45:10.790
&gt;&gt; Maria Schneider: Yeah.

00:45:10.790 --> 00:45:12.090
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum: Yeah.

00:45:12.090 --> 00:45:13.390
&gt;&gt; Maria Schneider:
Well, he was very open.

