wrote down a poem and he put it

00:46:08.680 --> 00:46:12.180
on a postcard, and sent it
to Jim Harrison, his friend.

00:46:12.180 --> 00:46:14.110
And then the next day, and it kind

00:46:14.110 --> 00:46:17.220
