man with the moon on a leash."

00:46:40.770 --> 00:46:44.700
So, you know, it's just
such beautiful imagery.

00:46:44.700 --> 00:46:50.110
And so, I was so scared for him
to hear the music because I knew

00:46:50.110 --> 00:46:54.620
that these poems were so for him.

00:46:54.620 --> 00:46:58.190
You know, they had to be so
close to his heart, you know.

00:46:58.190 --> 00:47:01.800
I'm sure all of his poetry
is, but I was just terrified.

00:47:01.800 --> 00:47:05.700
And I got up one morning
early, you know,

00:47:05.700 --> 00:47:08.620
and I glanced at --
Because I just sent it.

00:47:08.620 --> 00:47:12.460
I FedEx'ed it to him,
and there was an email

00:47:12.460 --> 00:47:15.600
